      • setShowDialogs

        public void setShowDialogs​(boolean showDialog)
        Whether or not CalcServerProxy should notify the user (via dialog) of failed connections to SnapDB and Execution Monitor.
        Parameters:
        showDialog - True - Failure dialogs are shown. False - Failure dialogs are not shown.

                                         java.lang.String folderPath,

      • retrieveFile

        public int retrieveFile​(java.lang.String folderPath,
                        java.lang.String name,
                        java.lang.String[] arguments,
                        FileRequestResponse response)
        Retrieves a file from the calculation server.
        Parameters:
        folderPath - a String containing the full path to the job from which to retrieve the specified file
        name - a String containing the name of the desired file This typically contains the key used by the server plug-in to refer to the desired file in the job's CJF.
        arguments - a String[] containing the code-specific arguments to retrieve file.
        response - the FileRequestResponse in which to store the retrieved file.
        Returns:
        0 Success, -1 Run not found, -2 Plug-in not found, -100 block read failure
